 ############################
 XTERM CONFIG
 ############################

  To configure XTerm create the file 
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | ~/XTerm								|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------

 add there the next strings
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | XTerm*background: white        					|
 | XTerm*foreground: black        					|
 | XTerm*faceName: DroidSansMono  					|
 | XTerm*faceSize: 11             					|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
